page.title: 09PATHHEAD:FAMILY LIFE 2
page.content:
FRESH FISH FOR HIS SUPPER.HE WATCHED T.V FOR TWO HOURS THEN WENT TO BED.
MRS COATS MY MUM GOT UP ROUND ABOUT 08:30.SHE MADE NICOLA AND I SOME BREAKFAST.AT 10:00 SHE WENT SHOPPING TO DALKEITH. SHE BOUGHT ME SOME MAGGOTS SO I COULD GO FISHING.SHE ARRIVED BACK AT 11:15. AFTER SHE HAD EATEN HER DINNER MY MUM WASHED AND THEN WAXED HER CAR.THEN SHE DID THE IRONING.AT 18:30 WE HAD OUR TEA.MY MUM DID SOME MORE HOUSE WORK, COOKED MY DAD'S SUPPER THEN WATCHED THE T.V LATER AT NIGHT.
LINDSAY COATS
AT ABOUT 07:15 I GOT UP.AT 09:00 I ARRIVED HOME FROM DELIVERING PAPERS.I THEN WENT TO THE FOOTBALL PITCH WITH MY DAD.WHEN HE HIT THE GOLF BALLS I
